metadata.name: Silly Gecko #1
metadata.description: Silly Gecko Gang is a collection of programmatically, randomly generated NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain. Silly Geckos, only 4444 out of millions of different combinations. All Silly Gecko's are unique. Each Silly Gecko is comprised of a unique skin, hat, face, mouth, eyes, outfit and accessories. Website: https://www.sillygeckogang.com Discord: https://discord.gg/sillygeckogang Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/SillyGeckoGang
